headline: How Shifting Analyst Targets Are Rewriting The Story For Realty Income (O)
summary: The latest tweak to Realty Income’s fair value estimate, moving from US$63.77 to US$64.31 per share, lines up closely with the refreshed US$60 price target that sits at the center of current debate around the stock. Some market participants point to recent rating upgrades and Q3 2025 sector commentary as support for a slightly higher target, while more cautious voices highlight that clustered price targets and an Equal Weight stance suggest limited potential if execution wobbles. Stay tuned...
